data.description: What an opportunity to own your own home on Wellesley Island. This home features, an open kitchen to living room, 2 bedrooms, laundry is in bathroom. Full basement. There are 2 buildings in the back. One is a bunkhouse with 2 bedrooms and a half bath with a sitting area. The other is a big open room. Both buildings are fully insulated with electric, but not heated. There is a very nice deck to entertain your guests or just to sit and relax. This home also offers a 5 foot pool (installed professionally) with a large deck for you and your guests. There is an area fenced in for the garden you always wanted. This is truly a must see! Listing agent is owner, NYS licensed Associate Broker. Call for your appointment!!!
